{"tid":1485941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我有個瘋狂諗法。","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:30:26.000Z","uid":175872,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db67fcf369b952d02e5b808f791288e22e7c7221","tid":1485941,"uid":175872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:19:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">敵進我退！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然呢加啲狗派咁多鬼，一於你地班勇武抖一抖，就好似出老解個句「出老解咪番屋企訓」，等班鬼自己係前面圍威喂，然後同自己啲伙記對侍。我地係後面或者睇live係到食花生但佢地自己打自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住呀mon post狗</span></span><br />\n你派得愈多鬼，同埋你打我地愈激，自自然就會有勇武想升級，想更加攬炒。到時老解一落黎，我地仲未驚個陣，你地膊頭粒花或者橫線就係咁先，直接比公安城管取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 20幾30k一個月88<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ba108662e6053c718c8dbf9737b8d8efeec590","tid":1485941,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:30:26.000Z","msg":"仲上緊警嫂嘅手足把握時間呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}